平讯号，欧洲领袖促先停火后谈判。","newsLink":"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20250813-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%AC%E8%A8%80%E4%BF%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E5%B0%86%E6%9C%89-%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D%E5%90%8E%E6%9E%9C","thumbnail":"","detailImage":"news/detail/rfi/2025/08/13/1755109034000.webp","sourceId":"rfi"},{"id":1755108137000,"createdDate":"2025-08-13 18:02","name":"法国国际广播电台","title":"双普会前视讯会 乌克兰欧洲明确自己立场","content":"在美国总统特朗普和俄罗斯总统普京8月15日在阿拉斯加举行双边会议两天前，美国总统特朗普周三与乌克兰总统泽连斯基和欧洲领导人举行了视讯峰会。","newsLink":"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2/%E8%A6%81%E9%97%BB%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/20250813-%E5%8F%8C%E6%99%AE%E4%BC%9A%E5%89%8D-%E6%AC%A7%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%BE%E8%A1%8C%E8%A7%86%E8%AE%AF%E4%BC%9A-%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%BA","thumbnail":"","detailImage":"news/detail/rfi/2025/08/13/1755108137000.webp","sourceId":"rfi"}]